items.description:
这是群星再世第六十七期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

不了解他的人，可能觉得黄炳耀只是小小的配角，仅此而已。但演戏不过是随便客串玩玩，编剧才是他的主业。黄炳耀确实在荧幕上的形象不多，他是那个《逃学威龙》“善良之枪”的主人警察署署长，《上海滩赌圣》“夺命剪刀脚”王局长。黄炳耀擅长编写喜剧，创作过超多卖座的喜剧电影，而且很是经典。在香港电影典盛时期，黄炳耀、黄百鸣、王晶、张坚庭被誉为香港八十年代四大编剧。

1981年，黄炳耀编剧处女作《老鼠街》。然后与洪金宝合作，成为洪金宝电影御用编剧，同年编写了《败家仔》剧本，之后这十来年，创作了大量喜剧剧本。

洪金宝电影《人吓人》《群龙戏凤》《霹雳大喇叭》《东方秃鹰》《富贵列车》《奇谋妙计五福星》《福星高照》《夏日福星》《最佳福星》《五福星撞鬼》

成龙电影《龙的心》、《双龙会》

林正英电影《人吓人》《鬼咬鬼》《僵尸先生》《僵尸家族》《非洲和尚》

周星驰电影《咖喱辣椒》、《逃学威龙》系列，不止如此，还有许多经典港片《猛鬼学堂》《猛鬼差馆》《提防小手》《辣手神探》《富贵开心鬼》《西藏小子》《双城故事》《蝎子战士》……这些电影全是黄炳耀参与编剧或单独编剧的。

《大话西游》导演、编剧刘镇伟曾经这样评价黄炳耀：这个编剧是天才，他是天才，当时电影商如果一年出品180部电影，就有90部是他的。他影响了整个香港电影界。

1991年黄炳耀在德国寻找编剧灵感时，突发脑溢血去世，享年44岁。

items.name: 【再世】next life-黄霑
items.description:
这是群星再世第六十八期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

被誉为香港四大才子之一的黄霑，不仅是天才的音乐人，更是唯一一个被两位顶级功夫巨星揍过的倒霉蛋。上学的时候表弟被人揍了，他气势汹汹跑去出头，到了一看顿时傻眼，发现对方竟然是学校的猛人李小龙，表弟就在身后看着，没有更好的办法，只能硬着头皮上。。。然后被打的鼻青脸肿，后来，李小龙和黄霑成为了朋友。

后来有一次喝多了，刚好碰到了成龙和洪金宝，然后他尿急就开始撒尿，故意往成龙身上甩，成龙推开了黄霑，准备动手，结果被洪金宝紧紧拦住没有动手，第二天酒醒后的黄霑上门给成龙道歉，后来还给成龙写了一首歌，这首歌成为《警察故事》的主题曲，俩人自此也成为了朋友。

大学毕业后，黄霑教了两年书，觉得太无聊，就辞职去策划公司当助理，彼时香港满大街都是洋策划和拗口的粤语配音。他心里想，我连李小龙都敢打，这口气我还能忍吗？初出茅庐的他大胆突破，提笔就写下一句人头马一开，好事自然来。短短十个字，便拉开了香港策划业改写的序幕，一战成名后他想既然策划词自己能写，那歌词应该也不在话下。

1982年，小鬼子篡改历史教材，企图掩盖侵略的事实，国内民愤难平。时任永恒唱片老板的邓炳找到黄霑，想请他写首国语歌，可他很少写国语，有人认为国语基本没市场，本来打算拒绝，可是当他听说是爱国题材的歌时，他二话不说，便一口答应，他联想到当时的时局，顿时满腔愤慨。笔下尽情地发泄着，很快就写下了《我的中国心》。

1991年，他从“宫商角徵羽”中找到灵感，一首《沧海一声笑》横空出世，古韵十足又挥洒大气。罗大佑都表示了不起。他发现这首歌用粤语和国语来唱，同样合乎腔调、洒脱豪放。尽管被后人翻唱无数次，可最经典的就属徐克、罗大佑与他合录的那一版。

更有《男儿当自强》《长路漫漫伴你闯》《狮子山下》《笑看风云》《上海滩》《 我的中国心》《忘尽心中情》《倩女幽魂》《两忘烟水里》《万水千山纵横》等经典曲目。

2004年，一代音乐奇才黄霑因肺癌与世长辞，享年63岁。

items.description:
Ara ara~

"Hime-style", "yamato nadeshiko", "wallflower". The look has many names, but it's an iconic Japanese style.

Very long, straight hair with blunted bangs and a hime cut at the front. Often found cascading over the shoulders or body, or gathering into silky pools on the floor.

Use the main tag hime style to enable the look and then use secondary tags like straight hair, hime cut and blunted bangs to sharpen the lines as needed.
cascading hair, draped hair and flowing hair also have noticable effects in most cases.

Trained on NAI.

Looking for a style I haven't yet created? I'm always looking for new ideas so let me know in the comments.

Strawberry is a style for creating cartoon characters with bright colors. It is oriented towards bright and vivid coloring, focusing on facial expressions. The LoRA has been created mixing other LoRAs and AI generated pictures. It has also been trained over NSFW pictures.

As for all my other models, this LoRA has not been created to mimic a specific style.

This LoRA has been trained using Mistoon_Anime_v2 as a base, so if you want to get results similar to mine, I recommend you to use that model.

This LoRA also works very well with my Mistoon_Sapphire_v2 checkpoint.

I haven't used this LoRA on other checkpoint, but feel free to share your results in the gallery.

In the past few months I've had a lot of people asking me why their pictures are not as detailed or clean as mine. I've written a few articles about SD, but if you want to learn my exact workflow I highly recommend you to check out my latest one: My Workflow

If you want to test this (or other models), I have made an extension to help me create pictures using a variety of different tags. The previews images have been generated using my custom extension Ranbooru which scrapes tags from random images on gelbooru, safebooru and rule34.

If you want to learn more about my workflow, check out the guides below.

items.name: 🦋 Butterfly (advanced version of Fidelity)
items.description:
✨️ How to get best results

  1. Use "Restart" sampler with 12 steps!

  2. Generate an image until you are happy regularly with ADetailer (always use it, trust me)

  3. Put the output into txt2img's ControlNet 1.1 with Lineart Realistic and "Priorize Prompt" setting.

  4. Turn on High Res fix with Latent Nearest Exact and denoising strength 0.6 and scale factor 2.

  5. Generate the new image. You can tweak the prompt to change colors optionally, since Lineart only uses the edges

ℹ️ About model

A model mix with multiple of my own trainings. Semi-realism with possible perfect nudity (no clothing artefacts) and simultaneously really good clothing.

  • female portraits of all types, including fashion design and full nudity

  • female full body

  • clean background for concepting

  • extremely good at turning super simple prompts and super complex prompts alike into coherent images: you can just write a three word positive and one word negative prompt and get good results

  • generate both flat chests and large ones (I made sure to preserve the big booba possibilities but by default it's not very noticeable)

🚩 Rules

  1. Don't generate kids in any suggestive way

  2. Have fun and stay creative :)

items.name: RealMix XL
items.description:
Merge of different SDXL photo models and loras.

No refiner or upscaler was used on any of the images.

If you want a good looking Midjourney-like image with a short prompt and no negative prompt set clip skip to 2, but if you want more control over the image and you're using a negative prompt then you can set clip skip to 1.

Recommended settings for 1.0:

  • Sampler: DPM++ 2M SDE Karras or Euler

  • CFG: 6-10

  • Steps: 30 or more

Recommended settings for 1.5:

  • Sampler: DPM++ 2M SDE Karras or DPM++ SDE Karras

  • CFG: 6-10

  • Steps: 30 or more

Most of the prompts are originally from Midjourney 🤣
